      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ec527-102">穩定的用戶端和服務 Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) 應用程式的控制代碼<xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>進行通訊時可能會擲回的物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ec527-102">Robust client and service Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) applications handle <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> objects that may be thrown during communication.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ec527-103">還有兩種衍生自 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 的例外狀況型別 (<xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException%601> 與 <xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException>)，用戶端也經常會碰到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ec527-103">There are also two <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>-derived exception types (<xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException%601> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException>) that clients also often expect.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ec527-104">因此，為避免一般性 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 處理常式攔截更明確的例外狀況型別，請在處理 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 之前先攔截這些例外狀況。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ec527-104">Therefore, in order to prevent the generic <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> handler from catching these more specific exception types, catch these exceptions prior to handling <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="ec527-105">收到作業合約中指定的 SOAP 錯誤時，用戶端會擲回 <xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException%601> 物件，以回應雙向作業 (也就是具有 <xref:System.ServiceModel.OperationContractAttribute> 屬性，將 <xref:System.ServiceModel.OperationContractAttribute.IsOneWay%2A> 設為 `false` 的方法)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ec527-105"><xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException%601> objects are thrown on the client when a SOAP fault that is specified in the operation contract is received in response to a two-way operation (that is, a method with an <xref:System.ServiceModel.OperationContractAttribute> attribute with <xref:System.ServiceModel.OperationContractAttribute.IsOneWay%2A> set to `false`).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ec527-106">當接聽程式收到非預期或沒有指定在作業合約中的 SOAP 錯誤時，會擲回 <xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException> 物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ec527-106"><xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException> objects are thrown when a listener receives a SOAP fault that is not expected or specified in the operation contract.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ec527-107">當應用程式在進行偵錯，且服務將 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A> 屬性設為 `true` 時，常會發生這種情況。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ec527-107">This usually occurs when the application is being debugged and the service has the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A> property set to `true`.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="ec527-108">實作自訂通道與繫結項目時，強烈建議您的元件只能擲回衍生自 <xref:System.TimeoutException?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 的物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ec527-108">When implementing custom channels and binding elements, it is strongly recommended that your components throw only <xref:System.TimeoutException?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>-derived objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ec527-109">當您的元件擲回一個專屬於該元件、且可復原的例外狀況時，請將該例外狀況包進 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ec527-109">In the case where your components throw a recoverable exception that is specific to the component, wrap that exception inside a <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ec527-110">如需有關設計和使用 WCF 錯誤系統的詳細資訊，請參閱[指定與處理合約和服務中的錯誤](~/docs/framework/wcf/specifying-and-handling-faults-in-contracts-and-services.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ec527-110">For more details about designing and using the WCF fault system, see [Specifying and Handling Faults in Contracts and Services](~/docs/framework/wcf/specifying-and-handling-faults-in-contracts-and-services.md).</span></span>  
  
> [!IMPORTANT]
>  <span data-ttu-id="ec527-111">WCF 執行階段不會擲回<xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>，並不安全處理它離開 WCF 執行階段和使用者程式碼的進入點。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ec527-111">The WCF Runtime will not throw a <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> that is unsafe to handle at the point where it leaves the WCF Runtime and enters user code.</span></span>  
  
   
  
